  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nIs the following yul program supposed to be valid?\r\n\r\n```\r\n{\r\n  for {{let x for {} x {} { break }}} 1 {} {}\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nThe `break` is in the `for` loop body scope which itself is nested within a for loop init block.",
